}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== The '''ZyXEL''' logo, "45-401-000728", and "Made in Taiwan" is silkscreened :on the board in the FCC photos. Some (/ all?) production boards are made in China, and note it as such. :The FCC label states the default SSID is '''ZyXEL'''.
===Probable used PSU(s)=== Two power supplies are shown in the FCC photos - one for AC models :(may be more common, if not exclusively such) and one for DC models.
